{"type": "article", "id": 49071, "title": "贝克汉姆推出男士美容品牌，以及，Air Jordan 出了 Levi's 牛仔款 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-01-10T03:53:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5487, "name": "Jordan"}, {"id": 3120, "name": "Levi's"}, {"id": 443, "name": "贝克汉姆"}, {"id": 3112, "name": "Bally"}, {"id": 17433, "name": "K11"}, {"id": 25622, "name": "山东如意"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180110113433Clb1OkKSW2a0HIhd.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-01-08/china-s-ruyi-is-said-to-emerge-as-leading-bidder-for-bally\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>山东如意集团加入对 Bally 的竞购</strong></a> | 据彭博社消息，山东如意集团正在与卖方进行谈判，以 7 亿美元的收购价格超过复星、七匹狼、赫美，成为 Bally 的领先竞购方。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.gq.com/story/david-beckham-house-99-grooming-line\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>贝克汉姆与欧莱雅合作，推出首个男士美容品牌</strong></a> | 贝克汉姆将与欧莱雅合作，推出男士美容品牌 House 99。据悉，这次欧莱雅将从零开始推出独立品牌，贝克汉姆参与从命名到制造的全过程，该品牌的产品包括剃须、面部、身体、头发等多个品类。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-bites/adrian-chengs-k11-invests-10-million-in-ai-start-up\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>K11 投资人工智能公司</strong></a> | 日前，香港零售集团 K11 向一家人工智能初创公司投资了 1000 万美元。投资对象 ObEN 创立于 2014 年，专注于为消费者及名人创建虚拟身份，K11 的这笔投资将用于驱动 AI 技术发展，它可以模拟人的声音、脸和个性。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/01/09/rick-owens-unveils-birkenstock-collaboration-los-angeles-store-shoes-footwear-fashion/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rick Owen 首次与 Birkenstock 合作，推出了马毛款的拖鞋。 </a></p><p>以 Birkenstock 的经典款式 Arizona、Madrid 和 Boston 为原型，Rick Owen 加入了全新的马毛元素，这双合作款将跟随 Birkenstock 在各地的 BIRKENSTOCK BOX 集装箱快闪店一同出现。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110111028NviFO63wQeG2RU14.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110111024kQWRfKdVwENJ3aT6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.740610\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110111024NXvob6BdRrsLQpi1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.724765\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801101110235KTvPWcktCzUGdeH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.617371\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-01-09/adidasoriginals-uasons/\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Originals 与日本品牌 United Arrows&amp;Sons 合作推联名款。</a>该系列包括 T 恤、连帽夹克、运动裤和 NMD 运动鞋，将于 1 月 20 日正式登陆双方各自的日本门店。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110111119aOpJ496BwFMokz1W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.495455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018011011111923GVoLpxi8yQ9w5l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.495455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110111119GhimCLqTbgQJ5Dzn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.495455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110111120EKgQaf27RAOrYH6F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.495455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110111125RPVXdY9MUxtmBuwT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.495455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110111121CrYtHAdqREfpZIB7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.495000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110111122Jdc7qlEM9onziX2a.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.495455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801101111217TfvCWyZ65Shqu0J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.495455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110111122mPW2osu8FrH1y5qt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.495455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110111122bo4g6asNGYML3zR0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.495455\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>2018 春夏系列里，Acne Studios 的 Musubi 包袋推出了两款最新设计，售价 800 至 1300 欧元不等。 </p><p>该系列包括带有纽花结饰的加大购物袋 Musubi maxi，配有短手柄和肩带的 Musubi mini，在黑色、栗色和蓝色的基础上，这一季还新加入了粉红色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801101123150Uqj12gdWNPfrHYt.png\" data-ratio=\"1.497881\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112203cV1uapy2IzkQOBg8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112206kyza20vq3KY7uHVS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112237feNBhm3l8yAkDvMH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>1 月 17 日，<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/529985\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jordan 与 Levi’s 的合作款</a>，一双牛仔布面的 Air Jordan 4，以及绣着“Flight”的双面牛仔夹克将正式发售。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112553oU5iD01Iu4Vwj6La.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801101125578vukR4wgQCrsVnE9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112544LqcJ8spKCVxlEtZb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112537UKCd24uBlNa8RzeD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112544G59gkhUyu3BReDqx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112545cviqFdK9RuaZDJXY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112548ZioJIvGfPXpVDMdN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112548gyS5fapx306qjAPQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112551O968lZvw7fDWg3ry.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112552o3WYnDKTSPCG8wql.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801101125557IJmHyzv98ZuEU3p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801101125575w8NhRi1DOAHTLje.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112557OukzqZcRGJMfeBIh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112559MPiWjUsXI6HfcdCF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>各大品牌纷纷宣布不再使用皮草之际，Celine 给它的经典款小方包<a href=\"https://popbee.com/accessories/handbags/celine-medium-classic-in-mink/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Classic Box </a>加入了全新的皮草元素。 </p><p>这款用貂皮、牛皮、羊皮制成的 Classic Box 包括米色和深蓝色，售价比同样是中等尺寸的 Classic Box 贵了近一倍。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112754XLiFmp81YUeoavJu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801101127541hsaD9TrCbnIwtMP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112754QvMqPIRlwa8X4VHD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112754NAd5TZRmqclnt20X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112754DTxgIvbXwaRr2MQP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180110112754Bm3TDifutehFJOY2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Jordan</p>"}